window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Guard duties, a peaceful realm, and plenty of beautiful women.</b></p> <p>After an accident cut my life short, a realm keeper gave me a second chance: be resurrected as a realm guard in another world. Bold heroics and brave adventures? Occasionally; this is a peaceful realm, and outside of guard patrols I need to help protect the beautiful women in the local community.</p> <p>If I can keep the tavern across the street safe, clear the local mine of monsters, and track down the local potion master's missing assistant, things might just work out.</p> <p>Accomplish all that, and I'll have plenty of time to spend with the curvy fox-eared tavern owner, the busty blonde who owns the local mine, and the fae alchemist living next door.</p> <p><i>Realm Guard features adult situations and undefined relationships.</i></p>"; 
